examples.en: He scored with a deflection off another player's stick.
The baseball player's small size did not handicap him in the least.
The star player's transcendent performance helped the team to a surprise victory.
The player's popularity has given him a great deal of leverage with the owners of the team.
The player's fulsome praise for the coach showed just how hard he was trying to be named captain of the team.
The sincerity of the player's penitence is questionable  he began to express remorse only after the suspension was handed down.
